title: 01/24/22 DPS Best Of

description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to the MMQB's Albert Breer about Tom Brady's future. Is this it for TB12? Rob Demovsky who covers the Packers for ESPN explains whether Jordan Love is the right guy in Green Bay. And Bengals Kicker Evan McPherson tells us from what distance he thinks he could have hit that game winner from. Did someone say 60 yards?
